  <brief_title>Pilot Study of Ketamine in Adults With Obsessive-Compulsive Disorder (OCD)</brief_title>
  <official_title>Understanding the Glutamate System in Adults With Obsessive-Compulsive Disorder With N-methyl-D Aspartate Antagonist Ketamine</official_title>
